<HEAD>Owner of Lost Money Identified</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A cache of 170 million yen ($1.2 million) found in a
safe at a trash-processing center three days ago belongs to a
retired newspaper executive who had forgotten about the cash, police
said Monday.
   Haruo Nakanishi told police he had earned made the money while
